lead_paragraph: A time few could imagine during the not-too-distant glory days of casino gambling has arrived in Atlantic City, where two casinos will close this weekend and a third will shut down in two weeks.

headline.main: Atlantic City Losing 2 Casinos, 5K Jobs in 3 Days
headline.print_headline: Atlantic City Losing 2 Casinos, 5K Jobs in 3 Days
